    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
      <locus from="5r"></locus>
      <title type="complete" ref="LIT4668Prayer#Monday">Protective prayer for Monday</title>
      <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
      <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS9602Turaev"></gap> ጸሎቱ፡ ለጴጥሮስ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ዘየዐቢ፡ እምሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ዘኃረዮ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ኲሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡
    ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ወጸውዖሙ፡ ለኲሎሙ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ወባረኮሙ፡ <foreign xml:lang="en">In the name <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS9602Turaev"></gap> a prayer of Peter, the chief Apostle of Him,
  chosen by Christ in front of all Apostles of Jesus Christ, Son of the living God. He summoned all His Apostles, stayed with them and blessed them.</foreign></incipit>
    </msItem>

    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
      <locus from="11r"></locus>
